    • com.atlassian.clover.api.registry.EntityVisitor

  • public abstract class EntityVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
    Callback handler for EntityContainer. The EntityContainer.visit() will call one of the methods in this interface, depending on the runtime type of the EntityContainer.
